node.text:
Anyone else ready for fall? We are getting excited for some cooler weather and all the delicious fall foods of course! That includes our Chocolate Zucchini Sheet Cake! It has 2 cups of shredded zucchini, so you have our permission to serve it as a side dish.

Head to our website, SixSistersStuff.com for the full recipe!

#chocolatecake #chocolate #sheetcake #zucchini #dessert #desserts #dessertsofinstagram #foodie #foodiesofinstagram #chocolatelover #sixsistersstuff #recipes

node.text:
Ahhh! It’s almost dinner! What are you having? It comes around so quickly every single day, and it’s summer! You don’t have a lot of time on your hands!

Don’t worry. We have the perfect simple and quick dinner recipe for you today, our Buffalo Chicken Sandwiches are the perfect quick and simple dinner recipe, we know you’ll love! 

You can make them in the Instant Pot or Slow cooker, or make and extra at the same time, and save it as a freezer meal for later! 

Find the full recipe on our website, SixSistersStuff.com

#easydinner #dinnerideas #sixsistersstuff #instantpotrecipes #chicken #buffalochicken #healthyfood #healthydinner #dinnertime #whatsfordinner #slowcookerrecipes #pressurecooker #freezermeals #mealprep

node.text:
Beef Tips and Gravy (one of our favorite freezer meals that you can use in your slow cooker or Instant Pot!)

It is a heat wave! And we do not want to turn on our ovens or grills, so we are surviving on our Instant Pots and Slow Cookers this summer!

These Beef Tips and Gravy are so yummy, full of flavor, and literally take only a few minutes to throw together. Also, we firmly believe this recipe is the secret to a happy marriage! 💕 It’s that good. 

Head to our website to get the full recipe, and save this video for reference! 

#sixsistersstuff #dinner #dinnerideas #instantpotrecipes #instantpot #slowcookerrecipes #slowcooker #beef #easydinner #whatsfordinner

I am also sharing the easy side dishes I am making that don’t require an oven (because it’s too hot!!).

Get the recipe over on Six Sisters’ Stuff or Google “six sisters grilled teriyaki chicken”.

https://www.sixsistersstuff.com/recipe/5-star-grilled-teriyaki-chicken/

We love a good freezer meal, and we even put together a list of over 100 Easy Instant Pot Freezer Meals, to get you through summer! 

Summer is just too hot for cooking in the kitchen (and even grilling some days) so we love to put our slow cookers and instant pots to use! 

For the full list of recipes, head to our website, SixSistersStuff.com and search for 100 Freezer Meals!

If you're as serious about peaches as we are, then you know the panic of knowing that you can't possibly eat all of the peaches that you bought from the adorable fruit stand on the side of the road, but cringing at the idea of wasting any of those beautiful juicy peaches! One fun way to use those peaches is in our Blueberry Peach breakfast pastry! This pastry is an amazing way to start the day, not to mention SO easy.
